divs: Sighting Detailsstanding out my back door talking to a friend.i looked up.i looked up and said "what the hell is that".i had no doubt what the object was and after she looked up she had no doubt either.disk shape silent flashing lights on the bottom solid object looked to be black slow moving west to east toward kent county airport followed a couple minutes later by a passenger jet. isaw this object maybe a minute and then it went into the clouds.my friend told me she had to inportant of a job to say anything and we didnt.i was in awe and i could tell she was quite rattled because we both know what we saw was real espically after the holland incident.the object went into the clouds.p.s.i bet if someone could get radar image from about that time it may be on there it did show up in holland.
Summary: disk shape with flashing lights on bottom solid object
